
### GET by ID
GET {{url}}/users/2

### GET all users
GET {{url}}/users/

### POST Create User
POST {{url}}/users/
Content-Type: application/json

{
"firstName": "Morten",
"lastName": "Jensen",
"password": "Morten123.",
"email": "test@email.com"
}

### POST Create Another User
POST {{url}}/users/
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Anna",
    "lastName": "Hansen",
    "email": "anna@email.com",
    "password": "Anna123."
}


### PUT Update User
PUT {{url}}/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "firstName": "Morten",
    "lastName": "Jensen Updated",
    "stationId": 1
}


### PATCH Change Email
PATCH {{url}}/users/1/email
Content-Type: application/json

"newemail@email.com"


### PATCH Change Password
PATCH {{url}}/users/1/password
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "currentPassword": "Morten123.",
    "newPassword": "NewSecure123."
}


### PATCH Change Role
PATCH {{url}}/users/2/role
Content-Type: application/json

"SOUS_CHEF"

### PATCH Assign User(Anna) To Station
PATCH {{local}}/users/2/station/1


### DELETE Delete User
DELETE {{url}}/users/2

###
